32
00:04:38,000 --> 00:04:44,000
Em lê mêze dikin... welleh qalibên kevir e! Çi hecer e!
Paqij e. Ev dîwarê kî ye xal?
 
Look at this... wow, stone molds! What stone! It is clean.
Whose wall is this, uncle?

33
